creator: Yokogawa Electric Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Sushi Sensor App is a tool for setting and status monitoring of the Sushi Sensor. Sushi Sensor is released by Yokogawa Electric Corporation in 2018.
Sushi Sensor App communicates with Sushi Sensor via NFC. This application navigates parameter setting, displays status and mesurement values.

◆Supported products
　XS770A Wireless Vibration Sensor

◆Tested Android devices
　 Nexus 5x(Android 8.1.0)
　 Moto X4（Android 8.0.0）
　 Moto G5S(Android 8.1.0)
　 Moto G6(Android 8.0.0)
　 Moto G7(XT1962-5)(Android 9)
　 ToughPad FZ-N1(Android 6.0.1)
　 ToughPad FZ-X1(Android 5.1.1)
　 ZenFone 5(Android 8.0.0)
　 ZenFone 5Z(Android 8.0.0)
　 ASUS_X01BDA(Android 8.1.0)

◆Known Issue
1. NFC communication sometimes fails on Android version 6. Please restart the Android device.
